''Alas, I am in love''

570
01:06:20,655 --> 01:06:24,284
''Let's paint the town red''

571
01:06:24,375 --> 01:06:26,570
''Let's show the world. . . ''

572
01:06:26,735 --> 01:06:30,250
''the magic of love''

573
01:06:31,855 --> 01:06:35,609
''Hearts speak. . . ''

574
01:06:35,695 --> 01:06:37,890
''flowers blossom. . . ''

575
01:06:37,975 --> 01:06:40,330
''in a world anew''

576
01:06:40,415 --> 01:06:43,566
''What I've done, I had to do''

577
01:06:43,775 --> 01:06:48,007
''Alas, I am in love''

578
