''If I'm swayed, am I at fault?''

680
01:21:35,335 --> 01:21:42,605
''Your eyes must be saying something?''

681
01:21:42,855 --> 01:21:50,125
''If I'm swayed, am I at fault?''

682
01:22:16,855 --> 01:22:24,205
''At your every footfall,
the seasons change. . . ''

